718→// ⟦axl_voices axo_guide axe_human_guide⟧
719→=== {rbtgo_depot_initialize}
720→
721→Completes one-time depot initialization: validates the
722→{rbra_rubric_github_pat}
723→and guides the
724→{at_operator}
725→through Developer Connect GitHub OAuth authorization.
726→
727→include::RBSDN-depot_initialize.adoc[]

  1→The
  2→{at_operator}
  3→completes one-time depot initialization after
  4→{rbtgo_depot_create}
  5→has provisioned infrastructure.
  6→This procedure validates the
  7→{rbra_rubric_github_pat}
  8→for mini-repo management and completes the GitHub OAuth authorization for the
  9→{rbtgi_source_connection}
 10→created by
 11→{rbtgo_depot_create}
 12→in PENDING state.
 13→
 14→This procedure is idempotent — safe to re-run.
 15→Steps already complete (PAT already valid, connection already COMPLETE) are skipped.
 16→
 17→// ⟦axs_inputs axd_none⟧
 18→
 19→// ⟦axs_preconditions⟧
 20→
 21→* {rbtgi_depot}
 22→exists (completed
 23→{rbtgo_depot_create})
 24→* {rbrr_gdc_connection_name} and {rbrr_gdc_region} configured in RBRR
 25→* {rbrr_director_rbra_file} contains {rbra_rubric_github_pat}
 26→* Operator has browser access for GitHub OAuth authorization
 27→
 28→// ⟦axs_behavior⟧
 29→
 30→. *Authenticate as
 31→{rbtr_director}*:
 32→.. Execute
 33→{rbtoe_director_authenticate}
 34→
 35→. *Load GitHub PAT*:
 36→.. {rbbc_call}
 37→{rbtoe_rbra_load}
 38→for
 39→{rbrr_director_rbra_file}
 40→.. {rbbc_store}
 41→`«GITHUB_PAT»` from {rbra_rubric_github_pat}
 42→.. If `«GITHUB_PAT»` is empty:
 43→... {rbbc_show}
 44→"RBRA_RUBRIC_GITHUB_PAT is not set in Director RBRA file"
 45→... {rbbc_show}
 46→guidance: "Create a GitHub fine-grained PAT at https://github.com/settings/personal-access-tokens/new with Repository permissions: Contents (Read and write), Administration (Read and write). Scope to the organization that will host vessel mini-repos."
 47→... {rbbc_fatal}
 48→"Set RBRA_RUBRIC_GITHUB_PAT in Director RBRA file and re-run"
 49→
 50→. *Validate GitHub PAT*:
 51→.. {rbbc_call}
 52→link:https://docs.github.com/en/rest/users/users#get-the-authenticated-user[GET /user] via `https://api.github.com/user` with header `Authorization: Bearer «GITHUB_PAT»`
 53→.. If HTTP 401:
 54→... {rbbc_fatal}
 55→"GitHub PAT is invalid or expired — regenerate and update Director RBRA file"
 56→.. {rbbc_store}
 57→`«GITHUB_USER»` from response `.login`
 58→.. {rbbc_show}
 59→"GitHub PAT valid for user: «GITHUB_USER»"
 60→
 61→. *Check Developer Connect Connection Status*:
 62→.. Construct connection path: `projects/{rbrr_depot_project_id}/locations/{rbrr_gdc_region}/connections/{rbrr_gdc_connection_name}`
 63→.. {rbbc_call}
 64→link:https://cloud.google.com/developer-connect/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.locations.connections/get[developerconnect.connections.get] for `«CONNECTION_PATH»`
 65→.. {rbbc_require}
 66→HTTP 200 — connection exists
 67→.. {rbbc_store}
 68→`«CONNECTION_STAGE»` from `.installationState.stage`
 69→.. If `«CONNECTION_STAGE»` is `COMPLETE`:
 70→... {rbbc_show}
 71→"Developer Connect connection already active — skipping OAuth step"
 72→... Go to step 7
 73→
 74→. *Guide GitHub OAuth Authorization*:
 75→.. {rbbc_store}
 76→`«ACTION_URI»` from `.installationState.actionUri` of the connection response
 77→.. {rbbc_require}
 78→`«ACTION_URI»` is present and non-empty
 79→.. {rbbc_show}
 80→"Developer Connect connection requires GitHub OAuth authorization"
 81→.. {rbbc_show}
 82→"Open this URL in your browser to authorize the Google Developer Connect app:"
 83→.. {rbbc_show}
 84→`«ACTION_URI»`
 85→.. {rbbc_show}
 86→"After clicking 'Authorize' on the GitHub consent page, return here and press Enter"
 87→.. Wait for operator confirmation
 88→
 89→. *Poll Connection Until Active*:
 90→.. {rbbc_poll}
 91→link:https://cloud.google.com/developer-connect/docs/reference/rest/v1/projects.locations.connections/get[developerconnect.connections.get] for `«CONNECTION_PATH»`
 92→.. Extract `.installationState.stage` from each response
 93→.. Poll at `RBGC_EVENTUAL_CONSISTENCY_SEC` intervals until stage reaches `COMPLETE` or `RBGC_MAX_CONSISTENCY_SEC` timeout
 94→.. {rbbc_require}
 95→`installationState.stage` is `COMPLETE`
 96→.. {rbbc_fatal}
 97→if timeout: "Developer Connect OAuth did not complete — re-open the authorization URI and try again"
 98→
 99→. *Final Validation*:
100→.. {rbbc_show}
101→"Running final validation..."
102→.. Verify GitHub PAT: repeat GET /user call — {rbbc_require} HTTP 200
103→.. Verify Developer Connect: repeat connections.get call — {rbbc_require} `installationState.stage` is `COMPLETE`
104→.. {rbbc_show}
105→"Depot initialization complete"
106→
107→// ⟦axs_outputs⟧
108→
109→The outputs of depot initialization are:
110→
111→- Validated {rbra_rubric_github_pat} — confirmed working against GitHub API
112→- Active {rbtgi_source_connection} — `installationState.stage` is `COMPLETE`
113→- OAuth token automatically stored in Secret Manager (managed by Developer Connect, not by operator)
114→
115→// ⟦axs_completion⟧
116→
117→Successful execution confirms the depot is fully initialized for
118→{rbtgo_rubric_inscribe}
119→operations.
120→The
121→{rbra_rubric_github_pat}
122→enables mini-repo management and the
123→{rbtgi_source_connection}
124→enables Cloud Build to access vessel mini-repos.
125→Proceed to
126→{rbtgo_rubric_inscribe}
127→to set up per-vessel build infrastructure.
128→

